Package src

COMP503 Assignment One: Technical School Application.

This package was created to determine the certification of a student, based on their provided transcript. The codebase was designed in an object oriented, scaleable way, such that much more functionality can be added for data computation based on the classes provided by this codebase.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Module
    Definition class of a school course, called modules
    ModuleTypeRequirement
    A class used for the Requirement checking of the TechnicalSchool certification.
    Requirement
    Holds a requirement for a student to be certified in the TechnicalSchool
    Result
    Stores the resultant grade for a module
    Student
    Stores the data for a student, such as their name, and their transcript
    StudentEvaluation
    Main application class for package, stores the user runnable code
    TechnicalSchool
    Holder class that stores the different Modules offered by the schoolm
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Grade
    Holds all values of grades and their boundaries.
    Level
    The level of a course
    ModuleType
    The type of study that a course offers, based on how the learning takes place
